# Build Rules

## Build Process

- Follow Next.js build best practices
- Ensure all TypeScript errors are resolved before building
- Run type checking: `npm run type-check` or equivalent
- Run linting: `npm run lint` or equivalent

## Pre-Build Checklist

- [ ] All TypeScript errors resolved
- [ ] All linting errors resolved
- [ ] All tests passing (if applicable)
- [ ] Environment variables configured
- [ ] No console errors in development

## Build Commands

- Development: `npm run dev` or `bun dev`
- Production build: `npm run build` or `bun build`
- Type check: `npm run type-check` or `tsc --noEmit`
- Lint: `npm run lint` or `eslint .`

## Notes

- Never commit broken builds
- Always test production build locally before deploying
- Ensure build output is optimized
